# Production APK build (standalone — no PC dev server required)
#
# Prerequisites:
# 1. Deploy the API once (see ../../docs/DEPLOY.md) and note its HTTPS URL.
# 2. Free Expo account: https://expo.dev/signup
# 3. Optional: Google Maps Android API key for map tiles on real devices
#
# Copy to .env.production and set your deployed API URL:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-api.onrender.com
# EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your-key

EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://loppisfinder-api.onrender.com
# EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
